      right: ["Term (37-42 wk): flexed posture, cracking/peeling skin, bald areas, deep plantar creases", "Square window angle 0° at term", "Brisk arm recoil with strong flexion", "Raised areola with 3-4 mm breast bud, firm ear cartilage with instant recoil"]
